{"tid":391424,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打出讓/介紹二手display卡","createTime":"2017-09-07T18:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T18:01:40.000Z","uid":145054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d32142b64b3770e619f79515c65c6dfe637f89d","tid":391424,"uid":145054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/08/020601_95955352b1d395d6176aa25c7cc75988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F08%2F020601_95955352b1d395d6176aa25c7cc75988.jpg&h=57c11f38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n部機今日無啦啦怪怪地   之後重開機  個畫面變左咁<br />\n打完密碼登入就黑mon   再重開再試都係黑間條登入黑mon<br />\n之後拎走左張display卡用內顯就正常入到window<br />\n所以我估係張display卡出左問題(唔熟電腦唔太肯定)<br />\n<br />\n用緊500w牛<br />\n底板asrock h77m-m<br />\ni5-3330s<br />\n16g ram<br />\n本身用緊張display卡係HIS ATI PCI-E HD6850 FAN 1G D5<br />\n平時電腦用黎上網  LOL  同埋多開模擬器掛手機game<br />\n想搵同本身果張差唔多/好本身果張少少既二手display卡<br />\n有無巴打割愛/介紹有邊道地方可以買到<br />\n畢直幾舊"},{"pid":"e86a405be43cd7b9bb69e2de2ac050fe90083873","tid":391424,"uid":133557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T18:50:25.000Z","msg":"GTX650ti 750Ti  比6850好小小 二手幾舊水已經有交易"},{"pid":"0f94b78f17ca31d910264e6d5a983a6aeee602c8","tid":391424,"uid":145054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T19:05:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GTX650ti 750Ti  比6850好小小 二手幾舊水已經有交易</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56211be501049d5946c5c845dcfd3d95d6d92d98","tid":391424,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T22:38:22.000Z","msg":"掉左佢買過部啦"},{"pid":"8a07a8b10d4d2ca981999ba183249f83ff651932","tid":391424,"uid":48022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T22:56:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掉左佢買過部啦</blockquote><br />\n人地壞graphics card咋喎,佢其他野暫時夠用就唔駛換住"},{"pid":"57d99ac9388ca45c364d729164eef6